{
  "server": {
    "tournamentMode": "round-robin",
    "teamsPerMatch": 1,
    "launch": "25s",
    "port": 12300,
    "backlog": 10000,
    "agentTimeout": 8000,
    "resultPath": "results",
    "logLevel": "normal",
    "logPath": "logs",
    "replayPath": "replays",
    "maxPacketLength": 65536,
    "waitBetweenSimulations": 5000
  },
  "match": [
    {
      "steps": 68,
      "randomSeed": 17,
      "randomFail": 0,
      "entities": { "standard": 15 },
      "clusterBounds": [1, 3],
      "roles": [
        { "name": "default", "vision": 5, "actions": ["skip", "move", "rotate", "adopt", "detach", "clear"], "speed": [1], "clear": { "chance": 0.7, "maxDistance": 1 } },
        { "name": "worker", "actions": ["request", "attach", "connect", "disconnect", "submit"], "speed": [2, 1, 1, 0] },
        { "name": "constructor", "actions": ["request", "attach", "connect", "disconnect", "submit"], "speed": [1] },
        { "name": "explorer", "vision": 7, "actions": ["survey", "attach"], "speed": [3, 0] },
        { "name": "digger", "speed": [1, 0], "clear": { "chance": 1, "maxDistance": 5 } }
      ],
      "clearEnergyCost": 2,
      "deactivatedDuration": 10,
      "maxEnergy": 100,
      "refreshEnergy": 50,
      "stepRecharge": 1,
      "clearDamage": [32, 16, 8, 4, 2, 1],
      "attachLimit": 10,
      "grid": {
        "height": 12,
        "width": 12,
        "instructions": [],
        "goals": { "number": 1, "size": [1, 1], "moveProbability": 0.0 },
        "roleZones": { "number": 1, "size": [1, 2] }
      },
      "blockTypes": [2, 2],
      "dispensers": [0, 0],
      "tasks": { "size": [1, 1], "concurrent": 1, "iterations": [5, 8], "maxDuration": [200, 400] },
      "events": { "chance": 0, "radius": [2, 3], "warning": 5, "create": [0, 0], "perimeter": 2 },
      "regulation": {
        "simultaneous": 1,
        "chance": 100,
        "subjects": [
          {
            "name": "Carry",
            "announcement": [2, 2],
            "duration": [70, 70],
            "punishment": [5, 5],
            "weight": 1,
            "optional": { "quantity": [2, 2] }
          }
        ]
      },
      "absolutePosition": true,
      "setup": "../../conf/scenarios/setup/06c-single-collect.txt"
    }
  ],
  "teams": {
    "A": { "prefix": "agent", "password": "1" }
  },
  "assert": { "metric": "submits_ok", "min": 1 },
  "//": "Cenário 09a-norm-carry (Eixo 9a / issue #19) — REGRESSÃO de norma Carry. Garante que o percept +norm(...) é recebido e parseado sem travar o ciclo do agente, e que a presença de uma norma Carry(max=2) não impede o submit. chance:100 injeta a norma no step 1 (announcement=2 → ativa no step 3). quantity=[2,2] fixa carry_limit=2: agentes com 1 bloco são sempre compliance (carry_limit(2), N=1 < 2 → norm_allows_carry=true). Punição 5/step — se houver violação, energia cai e agente deativado → submits_ok=0 → FAIL. Mesma geometria do 06c (coleta real de bloco).",
  "//regulation": "chance:100 + announcement:[2,2] fixos → norma determinística. ranges [X,X] tornam os sorteios de RNG irrelevantes (min=max). weight:1 (única subject → seleção trivial). Não usar chance<100 aqui: a seed 17 pode não sortear norma no step 1 com chance baixa."
}
